{
  "id": "5-2",
  "title": "Act 2: The Gaze of the Inorganic",
  "startNode": "main",
  "nodes": {
    "main": {
      "events": [
        {
          "type": "marker",
          "id": "ch5_act2_start"
        },
        {
          "type": "ui",
          "op": "blackout",
          "args": {
            "enabled": true
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "ui",
          "op": "fadeIn",
          "ms": 800
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 500
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "The drone swarm appeared on the fourth day.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 20
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 600
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "They were crossing an open abandoned industrial zone, ground rusted metal panels forming irregular terrain with hollow metallic echoes underfoot.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 22
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 500
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "{{characters.soren.name}} noticed first. Not sound—light. Several fine, rhythmically flashing points from the ruins' eastern sky edge.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 22
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 400
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "Initially three, then six, then more.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 18
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 700
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "dialogue",
          "speaker": "{{characters.elias.name}}",
          "text": "Drones. AI signal—not Ark standard, not Mondris format, not Solmaris either. <em>Independent</em>.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 26
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 400
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "dialogue",
          "speaker": "{{characters.alea.name}}",
          "text": "Withdraw.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 22
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 300
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "dialogue",
          "speaker": "{{characters.lyra.name}}",
          "text": "Where? No cover here.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 24
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 500
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "She was right. They stood in the metal plate center, nearest ruin structures far away. Drone flight speed far exceeded their running pace.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 22
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 500
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "dialogue",
          "speaker": "{{characters.soren.name}}",
          "text": "Don't move. Observe.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 20
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 800
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "The drone swarm arrived, hovering directly overhead in a loose surrounding formation. Over twenty units, each with red indicator lights on its frame.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 20
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 400
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "All indicator lights aimed at them.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 18
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 900
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "No attack.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 14
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 400
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "No warning.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 14
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 400
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "Just hovering, watching quietly.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 14
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 1200
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "That watching sensation was uncomfortable. Not from danger, but from the watching itself.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 18
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 400
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "Not predator watching prey, not sentinel scanning intruders.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 18
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 400
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "Something colder, more patient. Like an observer recording an ongoing <em>experiment</em>.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 18
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 1000
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "dialogue",
          "speaker": "{{characters.lyra.name}}",
          "text": "<whisper>What are they doing?</whisper>",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 22
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 500
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "dialogue",
          "speaker": "{{characters.soren.name}}",
          "text": "Recording. Sensor positioning isn't weapons lock—data collection mode. Gathering our neural signals, behavior data, or both.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 24
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 400
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "dialogue",
          "speaker": "{{characters.soren.name}}",
          "text": "And notice—they maintain fixed distance. Never closer, never leaving. Like there's an invisible boundary line.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 24
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 600
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "dialogue",
          "speaker": "{{characters.elias.name}}",
          "text": "They don't want to harm us. At least not now.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 24
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 500
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "dialogue",
          "speaker": "{{characters.soren.name}}",
          "text": "Or—<delay ms=\"400\"/><em>harming us would be meaningless to them</em>.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 22
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 900
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "The distinction between the two wasn't stated, but everyone understood.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 18
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 1200
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "The drone swarm hovered for a time, then dispersed silently, disappearing beyond the ruins' horizon like they arrived.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 20
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 500
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "Nothing left behind. Just four people standing on metal plates and a feeling harder to deal with than danger.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 18
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 1000
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "dialogue",
          "speaker": "{{characters.alea.name}}",
          "text": "Move. Continue.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 20
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 1800
        },
        {
          "type": "ui",
          "op": "fadeOut",
          "ms": 1200,
          "args": {
            "stay": true
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 500
        },
        {
          "type": "end"
        }
      ]
    }
  },
  "onComplete": [
    "complete"
  ]
}
